    "bio": "Intuz is a USA-based AI & workflow automation company with 16+ years of experience building custom AI-enabled workflow automations on n8n for SMBs and Enterprises. \nSpecializing in agentic AI, LLM integrations, CRM/ERP sync & multi-step automation across Healthcare, FinTech, eCommerce, Manufacturing & Real Estate.\n\nExplore our 30+ free templates or hire us for end-to-end custom automation tailored to your business.",
